videos.headline: Coastal's Marable turns on the jets for the 59-yard TD
videos.description: Grayson McCall dishes the quick shovel pass to CJ Marable, who takes it all the way to the house early in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Coastal's Marable turns on the jets for the 59-yard TD) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Marable strikes again for the Chanticleers
videos.description: Grayson McCall finds CJ Marable in the end zone for the 20-yard touchdown pass.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Marable strikes again for the Chanticleers) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Coastal's Marable gets a first-half hat trick
videos.description: CJ Marable rides the white line but stays in bounds to score his third touchdown of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Coastal's Marable gets a first-half hat trick) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Heiligh gets both feet in for Coastal TD
videos.description: Grayson McCall finds Javion Heiligh for the short 6-yard touchdown, adding to the Chanticleers' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Heiligh gets both feet in for Coastal TD) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Troy quickly responds back with a 41-yard TD
videos.description: Gunnar Watson passes up the middle to Reggie Todd, who spins out of a defender's grasp as he takes it all the way in for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Troy quickly responds back with a 41-yard TD) 2020/12/12 ESHEET
